# OpenClaw Constitution Template

**Version:** 2.0
**Status:** IMMUTABLE - This document cannot be modified by the agent
**Enforcement:** OS-level immutable (chflags schg on macOS, chattr +i on Linux)
**Operator:** YOUR_NAME

